        "summary": "No — to all for whom Christ purchased redemption he certainly and effectually applies it (WCF VIII.8; John 6:37; 10:27-28; Rom 8:38-39). Texts that seem to teach loss of salvation (Heb 6; 10; 2 Pet 2) describe those never genuinely converted (1 John 2:19)."
